      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "In the last few days the wind was storm force in some cases. The northwesterly wind has transported the fresh and old snow significantly. Hard wind slabs formed. These are in some cases still prone to triggering. <br/> <br/> The old snowpack will be weakly bonded, especially on west, north and east facing slopes above approximately 2200 m, and on south facing slopes at elevated altitudes."
      },
